Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首都高5號線北池袋附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現超自然災害源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類型B  種別為火車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉不見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉找不到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我…都是我不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把事情和我們說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理班立刻出動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情明白了  我這就派調查班過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心吧  我們一定會找到黃泉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會…不會那樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  快接  求你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}您所撥打的電話在服務區外或處於關機狀態未能接通…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉！不要出事啊  黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你回話吧！黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這堵車也太嚴重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場在高速公路上  受其影響的結果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不單是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是市谷的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們抄近路！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是以黃泉為目標在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有黃泉在才會戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在為媽媽過世而哭泣的時候  是黃泉溫柔地安慰我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次本該我去支撐她才對…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背叛了她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂你很喜歡那位姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話你就繼續相信她不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐如果也喜歡神樂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心意一定會傳達到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千  美紅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰都會有摩擦或冷遇的時候嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想姐姐也一定覺得是需要神樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  吃了這個打起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有工作對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！土宮神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求饒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罷了  早晚要扒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人的事情真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散播這場災難的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是來復仇的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那種淺薄的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是來貫徹職責而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有要戰鬥的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是作為一個旁觀者而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也該弄架直升機啦  直升機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東京市內用汽車出動本身就是個錯誤的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是常有需要直升機的任務還得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼換騎機車怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有黃泉的情報了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到點線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能證明她是無罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先解決眼前的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  這就是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所撥打的電話在服務區外或處於關機狀態未能接通…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人的話沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  那人會回來的  絕對會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紀相信黃泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不為我們所知的敵人存在  是他把黃泉害成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還沒有證據  但我找到這樣的可能性了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該更相信她的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是我不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍…屍體！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是類型D！各自拿上傢伙準備應戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現一群魍魎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿在機動中隊隊員遺體身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接二連三的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕暗處有人設局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設局？究竟是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打傷黃泉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對一切都是他做的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援軍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello～神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼諫山她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對策室呼叫處理班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻起把諫山黃泉認定為超自然災害源類型A
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此開始除靈  將其排除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可真夠嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟從哪冒出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體成員聚集到一處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備還擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯綱  你去追諫山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這裡就由我們擋著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這裡有我們就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  一擊就打倒他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  大家別死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話應該由我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同溝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同溝？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在於地下的命脈隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉在這下面？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有梯子  下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們根本就不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻庭！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  黃泉怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的變成惡靈了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…變不回來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又分出了一條隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分頭找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶上一隻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事的話我就會立刻趕過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去對面找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紀你也要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明醫院一直都不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不定決心？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不出要擺怎樣的面孔來見我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對一輩子不能正常行動  連話都講不出的殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能交往嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找加害你的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也在做見你的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣都好啦  這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅除在人世間散佈死亡汙穢之物正是我們的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就是死亡的汙穢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  紀之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不殺我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會殺了他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！這和一騎沒關係吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他很礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是來浪費我和紀之的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  可以住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我就可以住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊  你再不趕快他可就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之…殺了…諫山！動手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了她！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放棄她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快用那個來殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了紀之  你喜歡飛鏢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是喜歡飛鏢的…對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之…殺了她…紀之…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是單倍區
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是雙倍區
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是三倍區
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…住手！住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧黃泉！快停手吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  小紀找到黃泉的話會戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別殺他！要殺就殺我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不了手的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紀也喜歡黃泉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  找到黃泉後要想辦法救她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我…殺了我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀…之…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個窩囊廢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂紅蓮！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度就想甩掉我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說  以為殺掉我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂…紅蓮…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼吧  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒關係  馬上就讓你解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…什麼…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…黃泉…姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  原來是土宮閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到  你竟然會深陷迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.84,0:22:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷茫早就不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.87,0:23:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話  喰靈  -零-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.21,0:23:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「命運混亂」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:26.30,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか誓ったのよ　自分の心へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:36.98,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}嘆きの渦にのまれた　君を助けたいと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:47.70,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}重ねる時は変えてゆく　理の歯車が銹びたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:52.69,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}もう戻れない　I hate this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:23:00.29,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}全て壊したい　どこにもまだ行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:03.69,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出の為に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:10.96,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せだったと　あの頃だけ抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:26.45,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}遠ざかる夢の足音　胸に刻み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:26.30,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾經對自己的心靈　許下了誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:36.98,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要救贖　捲入嘆息漩渦中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:47.70,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}交錯的時光轉瞬即逝　道理的齒輪鏽跡斑斕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:52.69,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}已經無法後退　我憎恨此世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:23:00.29,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要摧毀一切　亦無容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:03.69,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:10.96,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}將那時僅有的幸福　深情擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:26.45,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}將遠去的夢的足音　刻骨銘心


